msgid "Each investigator resigned during Act 1 or was defeated"
msgstr "每位调查员在场景1期间撤退或者被击败"

msgid "You are rescued from the churning water battered and bruised, but thankfully still alive. After returning to the towering precipice where you began, you are pleasantly surprised to find Ruby and Andy chatting over a meal of dry rations. Rather than cut the reunion short, you resolve to make camp. Together, you pass the evening cracking jokes and sharing stories. Before parting ways, Ruby and Andy share their findings and compile a crude map of the ancient city."
msgstr "你被人从翻滚的水里救了出来，虽然一身的伤，但谢天谢地，至少还活着。你回到开始旅程的高耸悬崖，惊喜地发现安迪和露比居然对着干粮边聊边吃。你不急于打破重逢的喜悦，而是决定就此扎营。你们一整晚都在一起打超谈天，临别前，露比和安迪分享了彼此的发现，画出了一幅古城的大致地图。"

msgid ""
"The expedition members pass the evening sharing stories and cracking jokes. Even in spite of the city’s dour atmosphere, spirits seem to be high. You share your findings with Ruby and her companions while Andy attempts to make stew. She describes their difficult route to the vault, and advises you take the path up through the ancient court above, instead of the route she took through the silent factories."
"\"I’m pretty sure the factory collapsed behind us, anyway,\" Ruby says. \"If you take the path through the court, I'd recommend you steer clear of those 'pilgrims.' The whole city's crawling with 'em. I saw a whole mob shambling toward the colossal temple overhead. They told me they escaped an underground nest of some kind. Some of 'em seem to have come down with a pretty nasty fever, so I recommend you keep your distance.\""
msgstr ""
"探险队在玩笑和轶事中度过了这一夜。即便城里的气氛不佳，大家的精神却很高涨。安迪忙着烹饪炖菜的时候，你跟露比和她的同伴分享了发现。在她的描述中，通往秘库艰难重重。她建议你取道往上，走远古宫廷那条路，而不是像她一样，穿过寂静的工厂"
"“再说，我确信工厂在我们后面就全塌了，”露比说道，“要是你取道宫廷，我建议你避开那些所谓的‘朝圣者’。整座城里都是这帮货色。我看到一大帮子摇摇晃晃地朝顶上的大神庙去了。他们告诉我，他们是从某种地下巢穴里逃出来的，其中有人感染了相当严重的热病，所以我建议你离他们远点。”"

msgid ""
"The expedition members pass the evening sharing stories and cracking jokes. Even in spite of the city's dour atmosphere, spirits seem to be high. While Ruby plays poker with the more impulsive expedition members, you share your findings with Andy. He, in turn, recounts their trek down the sunken western wall and through the ancient foundations of the city."
"\"A rockslide stranded us in some kind of ancient crypt. There were mummified remains of some ghastly creatures—nothing like anything I've ever seen before. Otherwise, it's been pretty uneventful,\" Andy says, handing you a bowl of bland stew. \"Ah, but actually, a few days back, we ran into someone who was deathly sick. They refused to come with us. Said they were some kind of 'pilgrim' and that they came here to worship the god of this ancient city. Something named Cthulhu.\""
"The name \"Cthulhu\" rings in your ears.You have heard it time and again in your dreams. After the meal, you find yourself speaking it, under your breath, as you fall asleep."
msgstr ""
"探险队在玩笑和轶事中度过了这一夜。即便城里的气氛不佳，大家的精神却很高涨。露比跟有兴致的探险队员一起打起了扑克，你则跟安迪分享了自己的发现。他也讲了自己穿越沉没西墙道路，以及怎么通过城市远古地基的故事。"
"“一场岩石滑坡把我们困在了某个远古的地窖里，里面有某种可怕生物的干尸—那样的东西我从没见过。除此之外，就没什么稀奇的了。”安迪说着递给你一碗味道寡淡的炖菜，“啊，不过，几天前，我们遇到过一个病得快死的人，都那样了还不肯跟我们走，只说自己是‘朝圣者’，来这里是为了崇拜古城里的神灵，叫克苏鲁的什么东西。”"
"“克苏鲁”这个名字在你耳畔响起。你在梦里一次次地听过这个名字。餐后休息的时候，你发现自己不经意间，竟还在念这个名字，直到你陷入沉眠。"
